title: what college is REALLY like... dating, friends, comparing yourself & confidence

description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by social media star and college student Audrey Trullinger!  The gals discuss dating in college, being a musical theatre major, finding friends + being confident!  The gals also discuss comparing yourself to others at school, going to school during a pandemic and how to balance a busy schedule!
